      • getURLPattern

        public java.lang.String getURLPattern()
        Gets the url pattern for fetching other pages with two tokens ${startIndex} and ${size} which determine where to start the next page from and how many entries to fetch.
        Returns:
        a string with the format http://host:port/pathtocomponent.${startIndex}.${size}.selectors.format
